data.description: Welcome to 124 Channing Circle! This large home is nestled on a quite cul-de-sac and sits on 2 large lots, giving you plenty of outdoor enjoyment! This beautiful home has many extras! Besides the 3 bedrooms and 2 1/2 baths, you will be delighted to find many extras including a Bonus room with access to the kitchen.  The Primary bedroom is large with tray ceilings. Primary bath has dual vanities, dual closets, a stand alone shower  and a soaker tub. Just off the living area is the dining space and kitchen. The kitchen showcases a spacious snack bar, glass top stove top and an undersink water filter.   The half bath and  laundry room are near the garage entrance. The 2 car garage has a storage room for storing small things. If you love entertaining, You gotta check out this Game Room! Entertaining not really your thing?  You could convert this space into a glassed-in porch or outdoor kitchen space making it a great place to relax, hang out and cook.  Out back you will find a covered patio area, a large workshop and an above ground pool. The fully fenced yard ensures privacy and security. Security system and cameras stay with the home. Schedule your showing today and make 124 Channing Circle your new address!
